- Tolong lihat kemari.
- Sebelah sini.

684
00:51:57,790 --> 00:51:59,150
Bisakah kau menghadap ke depan?

685
00:52:04,080 --> 00:52:06,980
- Itu Who-joon!
- Who-joon!

686
00:52:08,170 --> 00:52:09,800
